** 📱 PURCHASE HANDOFF
*** WhatsApp Flow
**** Button: "📱 Order via WhatsApp"
**** wa.me pre-filled link (free, no API)
**** Auto message includes:
***** Product name
***** Brand (if set)
***** Selected size
***** Price in ₦
***** Strikethrough note if sale
**** WA Business App (free upgrade)
***** Away messages
***** Quick reply templates
***** Customer labels
***** Response time stats
**** "Ask a Question" button (2nd button)
**** "Save for Later" → WA saved msgs
*** Telegram Flow
**** Button: "✈️ Order via Telegram"
**** PHP Webhook (no persistent server)
***** Telegram calls webhook.php
***** PHP parses message + responds
***** Reads product data from MariaDB
**** Bot collects order info
***** Product name (from click)
***** Size selection
***** Customer name
***** Delivery address
**** Sends clean summary to seller
*** Sold-Out Handling
**** "SOLD OUT" badge on size
**** "🔔 Notify Me" button
**** Pre-filled WA: "Please notify when back in stock"

** 📦 PRODUCT SCHEMA
*** REQUIRED Fields ✅
**** Product Name
**** Current Price (₦ integer, no decimals)
**** Category (from 9 options)
**** Gender (Girls/Boys/Unisex)
**** At least 1 photo
**** At least 1 size + stock count
*** OPTIONAL Fields 🟡
**** Original Price (shows strikethrough)
**** Description (short paragraph)
**** Material (e.g. 100% Cotton)
**** Brand Name (e.g. Carter's)
**** TikTok URL (video link)
**** Season/Occasion Tag
*** 9 Categories
**** Newborn 👶 (0-3 months)
**** Baby 🍼 (3-12 months)
**** Toddler 🧒 (1-3 years)
**** Girls 👧 (3-12 years)
**** Boys 👦 (3-12 years)
**** School Wear 🏫
**** Special Occasions 🎉
**** Pyjamas & Nightwear 🛏️
**** Footwear 🩴
*** Size System (Mixed)
**** Age labels: 0-3M → 10-12Y
**** Number labels: 2 → 14
**** Custom: type any size label
**** Per-size stock count
***** stock = 0 → Sold Out badge
***** stock > 0 → clickable

-- 🛠️ TECH STACK (Hostinger)
--- Hosting Platform
---- Hostinger Shared Hosting
----- MariaDB included FREE
----- PHP included FREE
----- HTTPS auto (Let's Encrypt)
----- phpMyAdmin included
----- File Manager deploy
----- No VPS or extra server needed
--- Frontend (Ultra Lightweight)
---- Static index.html
----- All CSS inline in <style>
----- Alpine.js (15KB CDN)
----- Vanilla JS fetch() for API
----- Native loading="lazy" on images
----- No build step required
----- Total JS payload ~15KB
--- Backend (PHP on Hostinger)
---- /api/products.php
----- Returns product JSON
----- Filters by category/gender
----- Cache-Control headers
---- /api/status.php
----- Returns seller online status
---- /api/categories.php
---- /admin/ (password protected)
----- PHP session auth
----- Add / Edit / Remove products
----- Image upload (Multer equiv PHP)
----- Size Manager component
----- Toggle available/unavailable
----- Toggle online/offline status
---- /telegram-webhook.php
----- PHP Telegram Bot SDK
----- Handles webhook POSTs
----- Reads from MariaDB
---- config.php (outside public_html)
----- DB credentials
----- Admin password hash
----- WA number
----- Telegram bot token
--- Database (MariaDB)
---- products table
----- id, name, description
----- price, original_price (₦)
----- category_id, gender
----- material, brand, tiktok_url
----- season_tag, available
---- product_images table
----- Unlimited photos per product
----- sort_order (primary = 0)
----- Stored in /uploads/products/
---- product_sizes table
----- size_label + stock_count
----- Per-size availability
---- categories table
----- 9 categories + emoji + slug
---- seller_config table
----- seller_status (online/brb/offline)
----- store_name, tagline
----- wa_number, telegram_username
----- delivery_info (store-wide)

